{"tid":1217440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放咗150粒催淚彈","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:56:36.000Z","uid":103759,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27e1a9e6db9dc65f3e9ffcc58878f2ce7e304017","tid":1217440,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"一日150 粒？ 痴線㗎<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1132408596951207/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1132408596951207%2Furl%5D&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bc4c7221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1132408596951207/url]</a><br />\n【反修訂《逃犯條例》示威】<br />\n【盧偉聰：警方昨日施放150枚催淚彈、20發布袋彈及數發橡膠子彈】<br />\n【聞有警察在示威中對記者態度惡劣 盧望體諒】<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰指，昨天反對修訂《逃犯條例》的大規模衝突中，警方施放了150枚催淚彈、亦發射過橡膠子彈和布袋彈，均屬低殺傷力，亦有跟足指引。<br />\n<br />\n警方至今拘捕11人，分別涉及襲警、暴動等罪名，當中有部分人是在醫院拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一群在場採訪記者響應記協呼籲戴頭盔、面罩等裝備，不滿有警察在示威中對記者態度惡劣，包括以粗言指罵或阻撓採訪。盧偉聰表示希望大家體諒，又指自己對記者最客氣、最有禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #逃犯條例 #示威 #香港警察 #盧偉聰 #催淚彈 #橡膠子彈 #布袋彈 #記協 #記者"},{"pid":"4f8240f72f3a30929d17206a93517058fcc2e7a8","tid":1217440,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1132408596951207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1132408596951207&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=031ad287\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1132408596951207</a>"},{"pid":"8be236481abd1b5dadd17a6100d668ebfd96226a","tid":1217440,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b82b365532af7a1a7fe2fce4e773af8caf430c7","tid":1217440,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:03:29.000Z",